Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:06.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:11.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,下次可得挑對地點和對手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,你那邊也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,捕獲了盜竊的現行犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:24.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的  腰酸背痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,真傷身體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆是不懂的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是可靠的保鏢們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:38.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你之前送的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:45.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事  那種東西要多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過你們的工作就到今天為止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:52.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,明早就要出發去下一個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,就是要去西邊的街道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,是這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:03.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,那裡最近小偷很多不太安寧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:10.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,我能告訴你只有村裡人才認識的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是索瑪麗出什麼事也不好
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:27.80,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:27.80,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的這份躁動  是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:35.56,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:35.56,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像將臉埋入剛洗過的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:42.69,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:42.69,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥兒們吟唱著  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:53.75,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:53.75,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論走到哪  這道路都會延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:02:02.85,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:02:02.85,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牽手  更像是緊握這手指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:09.62,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:09.62,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:14.98,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:14.98,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空為毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:20.22,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:20.22,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌對面的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:28.66,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:28.66,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}為你指向盡頭之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:38.17,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:38.17,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才該說謝謝你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:57.98,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1510.133,1063.6)}守護之人與敵對之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆的手很大做起來也很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:10.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,做好了哦 錫佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆也一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知道爸爸會不會早點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,食物加上日用品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,大概就這些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:38.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,預備了這麼多  暫時就不用擔心物資了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,也賺了很多工資  路費充足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,再有輛合適的馬車的話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:46.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  想給小妹妹買禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,挺可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,肯定很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:01.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次見到防禦力這麼優秀的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知道索瑪麗喜不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,我覺得還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:10.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼  比起防禦力更注重防寒性的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒想到你還會為小孩子的衣服憂愁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,是這麼愉快的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過我不討厭現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:43.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:44.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,這個  送給爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,是索瑪麗給你的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,手環嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,是你親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:05.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  每天一點點努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,給我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,我在市場看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,雖然不是我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  不愧是父女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,想的事情都一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,和我一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:33.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,我才是  感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:48.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼  離晚餐還有一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,趁現在收拾下行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,大家是不是忘了很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,很重要的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,對  很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,錫佐  好冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:11.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂喂  很重要的事就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為雪都下這麼厚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼能不一起玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.55,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,我可不會輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.43,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,錫佐  給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,還真打到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,看招看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的  小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:31.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,我工作外出期間  我讓索瑪麗感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,我很感謝錫佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要和他學吊兒郎當了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.40,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,錫佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.70,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,沒事吧  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.95,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.12,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,我要來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.20,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥…哥雷姆  這會不會有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,你…不要過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:08.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,就在前面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,和情報一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,抓到後按人數平分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,久違的人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:20.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼  人類狩獵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:26.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,離他們到達沒剩下多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼他們會來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,和我們無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且這裡也沒有人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:36.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,有  就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,小妹妹  不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,我要保護她從這裡逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為  我們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,錫佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,亞巴希  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:10.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,你說過我做的點心很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,還想再吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,想和大家一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,作為保護你的理由已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂  你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是粗魯的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,喝口茶冷靜下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,鬼族？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,這間小屋應該有人類在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類？怎麼可能有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,是不是故事書看多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,給我找遍每個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:00.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,藏在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我都說沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,他難道要逃去人類那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,追上去  別跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,應該能順利逃出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,這裡像迷宮一樣呢  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,是舊的廢棄礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:46.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,我聽說穿過這裡的話  不用經過街道就能到達山的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:50.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們預定和亞巴希在那裡會合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,亞巴希沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:53.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,他沒弱到一下子就被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:57.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,居然自己決定做誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,這裝帥一點都不符合他的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,亞巴希很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,還有點心也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,錫佐很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,和你在一起也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:19.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們兩個都是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,快點走吧  亞巴希等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  錫佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,我稍微懂一點你的感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  錫佐  快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,若是為了守護那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,我便有種無所不能的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗真是一個不可思議的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,看來走得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,前面有座架在坑內的石橋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,只要通過那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,已確認獵人正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,要跑起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,難道亞巴希他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,和剛才的獵人不是同一群
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:26.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,找到了  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,一個接著一個  為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會找到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,小小的  看上去挺美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,把小孩交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,錫佐  別咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:10.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,得  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,好厲害  爸爸好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,遲早會被追上  趕緊向前出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,是因為使用力量了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:35.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,身軀崩壞的聲音無法停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,憑什麼不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類只配被我們吃掉或者賣掉  毫無其它價值
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:54.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,累了嗎  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法  畢竟平時這個時間都睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,看吧  爬上階梯後馬上就能到出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,出去過後  首先尋找能夠藏身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,也得趕緊和亞巴希匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:35.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,羅扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,我忘記了石橋已經斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:49.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,想要給你們送去新的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  羅扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,這裡邊就是出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:07.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:09.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,羅扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要把我們關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,立即放了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:25.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  你們馬上就能出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:29.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  索瑪麗不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:36.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為  人類可是很值錢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:42.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,難道  你也是獵人的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,我確實能夠破壞掉圍欄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是  要是再使用那個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的活動時間就又會被削減
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:02.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行  現在要儘可能久一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們去準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,離準備好還有一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,我給你們講一個你們不知道的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前  在一兩百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:29.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,我還是個孩子的時候  人類隱居在我們居住的不遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:36.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們互不干涉  在各自的村莊中平靜地生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:44.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,有一天  人類的小孩被野狼襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:49.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,然後  有一位心地善良的村民看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:55.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,那位村民拚死救下了人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類卻把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,但那其中肯定存在著誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  不僅那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,類似的事情上演了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:42.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,僅僅是因為種族不同  為什麼能夠做出那樣殘忍的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,逐漸的  我們明白了這是「歧視」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,之後發生了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:59.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們從中學到了  無法和我們相容的種族也是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:04.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,只有迫害人類  我們才能得到安寧地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:12.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類被迫害  被殺害  被販賣  被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,這全部都是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:19.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  索瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:29.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前  不知從何處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:36.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,來了一位奇怪的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:52.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,漂洋過海的旅人  遇見了頭頂犄角的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:59.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,竊竊私語著它們長得不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:06.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,然後統統把它們丟入鍋中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:13.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,隨意一口兩口嚐嚐湯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:22.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,紅色花兒  零落凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,是奇奇拉教我唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是從古相傳的童謠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:34.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,這裡所唱的「它們長得不一樣」你知道是什麼意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,指的就是「異形」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們把非人類之物  統統都用這個詞語所概括
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,在我們看來  人類才是異形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:50.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以你們全部都要被我們狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,聊天結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,到了切蛋糕的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,我要眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,我要腦子  那個可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,我要腸子  快給我腸子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,大家可要守規矩只拿自己的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,小孩子的肉可是很貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:21.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,還有  內臟我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類確實以前犯下了錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  那和索瑪麗沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,錫佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,快  把小孩交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,迫不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不會把索瑪麗交出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,還以為你能搞出什麼事情來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,快醒來  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的身體發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:16.04,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:12.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,住手  不要將索瑪麗帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,這麼纖細的脖子  一下就能切開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,那怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥  哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:02.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比較著並排的影子相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕陽甩在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘風而去的是那小小的祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什麼是永遠  什麼是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我還一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道當我抬頭仰望你時  你的側臉總是那麼地閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牽著手傳遞的這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論何時都在給予我愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}這不斷溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到傳達到給你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向著共同許下的諾言和未來  前進吧
